txt.en: 'If you believe the local gossip, I hear that you have some skills in combat. The children in town are eager to see your ranged skills! Why don't you impress the little ones who are over at the target area right now. They will be delighted to see you in action.'
Children can be found at the target range in the Rohan Kingstead neighbourhoods.\n\nYou should find the children who wish to be entertained.
Find the children who wish to see your ranged skills
'It is right in the center! It is right in the center!'
'It was so quick I did not even see it!'
'I want to be like you when I grow up!'
When neighbours work together, the households of the Rohan Kingstead will glisten upon the rolling plains.
Children can be found at the target range in the Rohan Kingstead neighbourhoods.\n\nYou should show off your ranged skills.
